    <Exec Command="copy /Y &quot;$(TargetPath)&quot; &quot;$(BepInExFolder)\scripts&quot;&#xD;&#xA;copy /Y &quot;$(TargetPath)&quot; &quot;$(ProjectDir)&quot;" />
